query:
INSERT INTO sms_messages (activationId, code, receivedAt)
SELECT id, smsCode, COALESCE(completedAt, createdAt)
FROM activations
WHERE smsCode IS NOT NULL AND smsCode != ''
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE code = code;
